</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<p><b>Soapstone</b> is a <a href="/Minerals#Geode_Minerals" title="Minerals">mineral</a> that can be found in the <a href="/Frozen_Geode" title="Frozen Geode">Frozen Geode</a> and the <a href="/Omni_Geode" title="Omni Geode">Omni Geode</a>.
</p>
