<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Bundles">Bundles</span></h2>
<p>Soapstone is not used in any <a href="/Bundles" title="Bundles">bundles</a>.
</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Recipes">Recipes</span></h2>
<p>Soapstone is not used in any recipes.
</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Tailoring">Tailoring</span></h2>
<p>Soapstone is used in the spool of the <a href="/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine" title="2 Willow Lane">Sewing Machine</a> to create the <a href="/Tailoring" title="Tailoring">Gaudy Shirt</a>.  <a href="/File:Shirt170.png" class="image"><img alt="Shirt170.png" src="/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/36/Shirt170.png/24px-Shirt170.png" decoding="async" width="24" height="24" srcset="/mediawiki/images/3/36/Shirt170.png 1.5x" /></a>
</p><p>It is a white dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed.
</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Quests">Quests</span></h2>
<p>Soapstone is not used in any <a href="/Quests" title="Quests">quests</a>.
</p>
